<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/views/user/css/login.css" />
  <title>登录</title>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="login-card">
    <div class="column">
      <h1>登陆</h1>
      <p>欢迎来到黑石博客，请输入账号密码！</p>
      <form action="#" class="sign-up-form" id="sign-up-form">
        <div class="form-item">
          <input type="text" class="form-element" placeholder="用户名" name="username" autocomplete="off" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-item">
          <input type="password" class="form-element" placeholder="密码" name="password" autocomplete="off" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-checkbox-item">
          <input type="checkbox" id="rememberMe" checked />
          <label for="rememberMe">记住我</label>
        </div>
        <div class="flex">
          <input type="submit" class="btn" value="登录" />
          <a href="#">忘记密码，点我重置！</a>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem">第三方账号登入</p>
        <div class="social-buttons">
          <a href="#" class="wechat">
            <i class="bi bi-wechat"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="twitter">
            <i class="bi bi-twitter"></i>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="github">
            <i class="bi bi-github"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="column">
      <h2>自然选择号欢迎您登舰！</h2>
      <p>如果你没有账号，你想要现在注册一个吗？</p>
      <a href="/register">注册</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script src="/node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery.js"></script>
  <script>
    $(function () {
      $('#sign-up-form').on('submit', function (e) {
        // 取消表单的默认提交事件
        e.preventDefault()
        // 当取消了表单的默认提交行为之后，手动发起Ajax请求，提交表单
        $.ajax({
          url: '/login',
          data: $('#sign-up-form').serialize(),
          type: 'POST',
          dataType: 'json',
          success: function (result) {
            if (result.status !== 200) {
              return alert(result.msg)
            }
            location.href = '/'
          }
        })
      })
    })
  </script>
</body>

</html>